The most poignant department is the memorial for the children built to commemorate the 1.5 million children who were destroyed in the concentration camps and gas chambers.
When the room enters, there is complete darkness.
Star sparkles.
And the names of the Jewish children and the countries in which they died were heard.
Ukraine is also mentioned there.
Doing something for health
The three main recreation areas of Israel are located on the shores of the Mediterranean Sea, the Red Sea and the Dead Sea.
In each of the three places there are swimming pools, water parks, dolphins and oceanaries.
Amazingly, in the Red Sea, the water temperature is also bathed in the winter months, as the water temperature is not below 21 °C and the air warms up to 23 °C.
The Dead Sea is even warmer and bathed all year round.
