Its turquoise blue water has a high salt content and thus even non-swimper can carry easily on the surface.
The surrounding landscape is indescribably beautiful.
Visitors come here for treatments using salt water (natural salt soles) and healing mud, as well as for the treatment of skin inflammation, allergies, asthma, eczema, arthritis, bronchitis, sugar disease and for the calming of damaged nerves.
The Secrets of Age Touch
