As a teenager, these children immediately take the first opportunity to earn money.
"It is difficult without language skills," they admit.
"You feel humiliated and inferior."
Citizensrechtler emphasizes the following important aspect with regard to the law.
Only migrants with legal status must take the test.
If you do not have this status, there is no examination and therefore no official work.
In the meantime, most of the guest workers continue to stay illegally in Russia.
"Welcome welcome" or "admission for unauthorised"
