It is true that the collaboration with well-known singers has helped us, and we have also started to actively advertise for ourselves.
We have become aware that if you do something and you can't see it outwardly, your own performance does not exist in a certain sense.
Thanks to the EU funding funds, we can also afford good readers, high-quality equipment and others.
